code: import axios from"axios";var cors=require('cors');var baseURL="http://localhost:2410";function get(url){return axios.get(baseURL+url);}function post(url,obj){return axios.post(baseURL+url,obj);}function put(url,obj){return axios.put(baseURL+url,obj);}function deleteApi(url){return axios.delete(baseURL+url);}export default{get:get,post:post,put:put,deleteApi:deleteApi};
